      "metadata": null,
      "package_id": "galileo_coarse",
      "parameters": [],
      "provenance": null,
      "representative_lcn": null,
      "type": "claim"
    },
    {
      "content": "在不同介质中比较轻重物体的下落，介质越稠密速度差异越明显；越稀薄差异越不明显。",
      "content_hash": "9e090334d4bb55c4b3090d50a016f1e15bbbfeb65ff4c11997260f16137c0ddd",
      "id": "lcn_9ed0f784c1523feb",
      "local_members": null,
      "metadata": null,
      "package_id": "galileo_coarse",
      "parameters": [],
      "provenance": null,
      "representative_lcn": null,
      "type": "claim"
    },
    {
      "content": "在空气中，金球、铅球、铜球等重材料球从100腕尺落下，金球领先铜球不超过四指。",
      "content_hash": "00b33ea8900677cdc7959dba51969adf5d49916cdd9a4e47f0676b6d9d974564",
      "id": "lcn_95fab96520b2a2d6",
      "local_members": null,
      "metadata": null,
      "package_id": "galileo_coarse",
      "parameters": [],
      "provenance": null,
      "representative_lcn": null,
      "type": "claim"
    },
    {
      "content": "斜面实验：不同重量的球沿抛光沟槽滚下，所经距离之比等于时间之比的平方，与球重量无关。",
      "content_hash": "ce317a963c5db89cef35901c8fde21ce49946b1229c84b42473ae421d3fb41e9",
      "id": "lcn_1966c6e7c19411b9",
      "local_members": null,
      "metadata": null,
      "package_id": "galileo_coarse",
      "parameters": [],
      "provenance": null,
      "representative_lcn": null,
      "type": "claim"
    },
    {
      "content": "物体下落速度与其重量成正比：重物比轻物下落更快。",
      "content_hash": "04d12524a96aa62d944af0e7ea05f62354523b8141297a61293708f5f3893381",
      "id": "lcn_70a1e93d4c535b62",
      "local_members": null,
      "metadata": null,
      "package_id": "galileo_coarse",
      "parameters": [],
      "provenance": null,
      "representative_lcn": null,
      "type": "claim"
    },
    {
      "content": "假设重物下落更快，将重球H与轻球L绑在一起，L拖拽H，复合体HL速度应慢于H单独下落。",
      "content_hash": "b624f2573110860b8c95160a11110b56b759846a1029ebaa93ef672e5598964b",
      "id": "lcn_f5cfb269d7e6e3cf",
      "local_members": null,
      "metadata": null,
      "package_id": "galileo_coarse",
      "parameters": [],
      "provenance": null,
      "representative_lcn": null,
      "type": "claim"
    },
    {
      "content": "假设重物下落更快，复合体HL总重量大于H，因此HL速度应快于H单独下落。",
      "content_hash": "fa7e2bb46c20e1d24b255fbfa4e9a11b4f113c2b33440bbc7927ec0e40b8b05e",
      "id": "lcn_cf396f1d946ef45b",
      "local_members": null,
      "metadata": null,
      "package_id": "galileo_coarse",
      "parameters": [],
      "provenance": null,
      "representative_lcn": null,
      "type": "claim"
    },
    {
      "content": "T1与T2互相矛盾：复合体HL不能同时慢于H又快于H。",
      "content_hash": "62c0ad9a1d5021a3a7f89ebc4374350ad47ed1fb07fa2f67fffc56a56d745b4a",
      "id": "lcn_ab561171566f1c0d",
