      "package_id": "galileo_coarse",
      "parameters": [],
      "provenance": null,
      "representative_lcn": null,
      "type": "claim"
    },
    {
      "content": "在真空中也应重者更快（A的推论应用于真空条件）。",
      "content_hash": "be76524c1b65717a7f7f86a4c29cc34c30ef5f58f71398835242feb0f87073b6",
